data.description: Experience the comfort in this impeccably remodeled 4-bedroom, 2-bathroom home nestled on a .86-acre lot. The heart of this home is the kitchen, adorned with granite countertops and stainless steel appliances. Entertain guests easily in the open-concept living spaces, where the seamless flow between rooms creates an inviting atmosphere. The master suite is reminiscent of a spa-like retreat. Tile floors throughout the home for easy cleanup and maintenance. Plenty of room for toys, gardening & 2 sheds for hobbies or storage.
